      <title>随着南非投票临近，非国大在捐款活动方面落后于主要竞争对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/anc-lags-main-rival-in-donation-drive-as-south-africa-vote-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非主要反对党民主联盟在今年全国选举前夕获得了比执政的非洲人国民大会及其其他竞争对手更多的捐款，从而支撑了其竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/anc-lags-main-rival-in-donation-drive-as-south-africa-vote-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
